{"tid":401044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無良視光師　醫療券當提款機","createTime":"2017-09-15T10:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T10:10:04.000Z","uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4cd2ab6bc1af5d25009e807f7ab5bf26f5941711","tid":401044,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:01:15.000Z","msg":"醫療券恒常化後，2016年用於眼部檢查的支出較2014年急增11倍，而今年首8個月的交易金額已達1.3億港元。視光業內人士踢爆，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有已登記提供醫療券服務的第一部分註冊視光師在5至6間眼鏡舖「掛單」，而有關眼鏡舖會先安排普通視光師為長者進行驗眼及配眼鏡工作，「掛單」視光師只要每周到相關眼鏡舖數小時申報診症金額，便可月入高達10萬元。亦有無參與醫療券的眼鏡舖允許收取醫療券，甚至聲稱可在申報醫療券交易時造假</span></strong>。關注長者權益協會敦促衞生署正視問題，以免長者的資源被「榨乾」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170915/photo/bkn-20170915050029714-0915_00822_001_04b.jpg?20170915053400\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170915%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170915050029714-0915_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20170915053400&h=8390fcee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/hknews/20170915/20170915050030lc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Fhknews%2F20170915%2F20170915050030lc.html&d=0%2FEK%2B6YI7CJB0OEbmVghl57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=f99ad478\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/hknews/20170915/20170915050030lc.html</a><br />\n<br />\n廢老配眼鏡用醫療券<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95131408f615704f0ff2f698036c4e9730e3140","tid":401044,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:02:09.000Z","msg":"食到條水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d49f4ed9240345276d447bb5c1bc14c0061781","tid":401044,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:07:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食到條水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif